3. **## Why it's shaped this way** — 2–3 sentences linking the flow to
   the archetype: why this structure makes sense for a service / cli /
   etc. Do not invent decisions; restrict yourself to observations the
   flow itself supports.
4. **## Where to read next** — a short bulleted list of 2–4 file paths
   the reader should open after this page, pulled from the flow hops
   above. Each bullet gets a half-sentence reason ("the boundary where
   request becomes domain object", etc.).

